name: heavensgotaplanforu-2
description:
October 2021 // she's dancing and stretching — bones cracking, muscles flexing, synapses unnerved, everything's in equilibrium — the soul is re-energized. Not dissociating, but definitely tapped into her insides, she notes that the only way is up. Everything inside and out is flowing yet staying still; she's patient with her pace and intuition and feeling every feeling. All she's wearing are pearl chains and a torso brace and that's all she really needs; the love in her body carries the rest.

a still of an GIF. a unique iteration of four.
